Class LinkedListWithIterator<T>

java.lang.Object
LinkedListWithIterator<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<T>, ListInterface<T>, ListWithIteratorInterface<T>
public class LinkedListWithIterator<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ListWithIteratorInterface<T>
A class that implements the ADT list by using a chain of linked nodes. The list has an iterator. The class is similar to LList.
Author:
Joseph Siwiecki
